Popular rapper, Nicki Minaj, has confirmed she is pregnant. Nicki and Kenneth Petty are expecting their first child together. In a post captioned, “Preggers” Nicki in a yellow wig revealed the news with a baby bump image on her Instagram page. Her post has confirmed pregnancy speculations on social media. The award-winning rapper tied the knot with Petty in October 2019. The rapper had announced the news in an Instagram video.